graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Operator"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        PredictorCtrl[Predictor Controller<br/>Model Lifecycle]
        RuntimeCtrl[ServingRuntime Controller<br/>Runtime Provisioning]
        ServiceCtrl[Service Controller<br/>Endpoint Management]
        AutoscalerCtrl[Autoscaler Controller<br/>HPA Management]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Resource Validation]

        Controller --> PredictorCtrl
        Controller --> RuntimeCtrl
        Controller --> ServiceCtrl
        Controller --> AutoscalerCtrl
        Controller --> Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Components"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Java Runtime<br/>Model Routing]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Go Service<br/>Model Load/Unload]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>Go Service<br/>KServe V2 Translation]
        StorageHelper[Storage Helper<br/>Go Service<br/>S3 Puller]
        ModelServer[Model Server Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe]

        ModelMesh --> RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter --> StorageHelper
        RuntimeAdapter --> ModelServer
        RESTProxy --> ModelMesh
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        etcd[etcd<br/>Model Metadata Storage]
        S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS Certificates]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| PredictorCtrl
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtrl
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtrl
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Webhook -->|validates| ServingRuntimeCR
    Webhook -->|validates| ClusterServingRuntimeCR

    PredictorCtrl -->|manages| ModelMesh
    RuntimeCtrl -->|provisions| RuntimePod[Runtime Deployment]
    ServiceCtrl -->|creates| K8sService[Kubernetes Service]
    AutoscalerCtrl -->|creates| HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]

    RuntimePod -.->|contains| ModelMesh
    RuntimePod -.->|contains| RuntimeAdapter
    RuntimePod -.->|contains| RESTProxy
    RuntimePod -.->|contains| StorageHelper
    RuntimePod -.->|contains| ModelServer

    Controller -->|watches| K8sAPI
    PredictorCtrl -->|stores metadata| etcd
    RuntimeCtrl -->|stores config| etcd
    StorageHelper -->|downloads models| S3
    Webhook -->|TLS certs from| CertManager
    Controller -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus
    ModelMesh -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus

    Client[Client Application] -->|gRPC 8033/TCP| K8sService
    Client -->|REST 8008/TCP| K8sService
    K8sService -->|routes to| ModelMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RuntimeCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style AutoscalerCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
